full_title: Darling, I by Tyler, The Creator (Ft. Teezo Touchdown)
title: Darling, I

description.plain:
“Darling, I” is the 4th song on Tyler, The Creator’s 8th studio album “CHROMAKOPIA.”

The song is a journey through Tyler, The Creator’s reflections on love, freedom, and self-awareness, underscored by his complex emotions about commitment. Tyler’s introspective lyrics reveal his attraction to both love and freedom, feeling conflicted by the permanence of commitment and the temptation of new experiences. Teezo Touchdown’s verse adds depth, backing Tyler’s sentiments with his own struggles for fulfilment and individuality. With Bonita Smith’s grounding advice—"Transparency is key, be honest"—the track underscores the necessity of sincerity in relationships and self-acceptance.
